homepage            https://brush.sh

description         bash/POSIX-compatible shell implemented in Rust

long_description    \
    brush \(Bo\(u\)rn\(e\) RUsty SHell\) is a POSIX- and bash-compatible \
    shell, implemented in Rust. It\'s built and tested on Linux, macOS, and \
    WSL. brush is functional for interactive use as a daily driver\! It \
    executes most sh and bash scripts we've encountered

